  "userRequest": "Project context: Can we create a mobile counter app? I have mockups to demonstrate the first page.",
  "description": "Built the CodeYam Counter iOS app (SwiftUI) primary screen: a giant numeral with four switchable, color-coded counters (tap a dot or swipe), persisted on-device. The increment button sits low and extends into an equal-quarter bottom row of SUBTRACT, RESET, and a SWITCH button that mirrors the layout for left-handed one-thumb use; subtract goes negative by default. ContentView is decomposed into nine section components, with CounterModel and CounterTheme covered by 14 unit tests and six application scenarios.",
